    "resolveState": "INIT",
    "cdate": "1781011715000",
    "comment": "<p>Avoid at all cost!</p>\n<p>This \"integration\" is the utter most garbage there is. Sloppily created (most likely AI slop), full of bugs, and far behind the CLI version or any other integration for other IDEs.</p>\n<p>Does not respect Planning Mode; it will code anyway.\nDoes not respect file system boundaries; it will access everything.\nDoes not work when executing something on a terminal; will say 'program did not answer' while it's still running, and it will not see the terminal's output.\nDoes not respect settings; will choose default garbage GPT model.</p>\n<p>DO NOT USE.</p>\n",
