    "id": 140218,
    "rating": 5,
    "isResolveRequested": false,
    "resolveState": "INIT",
    "cdate": "1780036397000",
    "comment": "<p>This is an extremely useful code generation plugin. Among all the plugins I have tried, I believe it boasts the best quality, fastest response speed and most reasonable design. I have decided to keep subscribing to it and wish you continued success. Thank you very much for developing this plugin, which has been a tremendous help to me. However, there is one downside: it does not support image uploads to utilize vision capabilities. This has created significant obstacles when I need to upload images to quickly generate reliable UIs or upload architecture diagrams to build frameworks accordingly. Do you have plans to complete this feature?</p>\n",
    "plugin": {
      "id": 17718,
