    "resolveState": "INIT",
    "cdate": "1779473649000",
    "comment": "<p>My opinion is that this plugin is simply fantastic, and I wholeheartedly recommend it to anyone who wants code generated on their behalf. It works quickly, is intuitive, and significantly speeds up a developer’s work. The only drawback is the credit limit for users of the free version and the need to purchase a subscription to use it without restrictions. I really wish the plugin had no limits and didn’t reset every 16 days. I appeal to the authors to remove these restrictions so we can use the plugin’s capabilities without interruptions or limitations.</p>\n",
